\left\{ X_n \right\}
 \left\{ Y_n \right\} 
 \left\{ X_n + Y_n \right\} 
P(X_{t_1} \in B_1 , ... , X_{t_n} \in B_n) = P(X_{t_1 + h} \in B_1 , ... , X_{t_n + h} \in B_n) \\ P(Y_{t_1} \in B_1 , ... , Y_{t_n} \in B_n) = P(Y_{t_1 + h} \in B_1 , ... , Y_{t_n + h} \in B_n)
P(X_{t_1} + Y_{t_1} \in B_1 , ... , X_{t_n} + Y_{t_n} \in B_n) = P(X_{t_1 + h} + Y_{t_1 + h} \in B_1 , ... , X_{t_n + h} + Y_{t_n+h} \in B_n)
